item.title: CVE-2021-25054|2024-08-03T19:49:14.539Z -- unknown -- wpcalc%20%E2%80%93%20create%20any%20online%20calculators
item.description: The WPcalc WordPress plugin through 2.1 does not sanitize user input into the 'did' parameter and uses it in a SQL statement, leading to an authenticated SQL Injection vulnerability.
